## Summary of Applied Optimizations

### 🔴 HIGH — Database & I/O
| Fix | Before | After |
|---|---|---|
| **N+1 reactions** (`db.ts` + `messages.ts`) | 1 query per message in list/search (500+ queries at max limit) | Single batched `WHERE message_id IN (...)` query → Map lookup |
| **N+1 file lookups** (`db.ts`) | Loop calling `get(id)` per attachment | Single `WHERE id IN (...)` query preserving order |
| **Sync file write** (`files.ts`) | `writeFileSync` blocks event loop (up to 50MB files) | `fs/promises.writeFile` — non-blocking async |

### 🟡 MEDIUM — SSE, Shutdown, Rooms
| Fix | What changed |
|---|---|
| **Duplicate `onAbort`** (`messages.ts`) | Removed the second `stream.onAbort` handler (dead code) |
| **Graceful shutdown** (`index.ts` + `stream.ts`) | `heartbeatInterval` exported; `SIGTERM`/`SIGINT` clears it + closes server |
| **Double `listRooms()`** (`rooms.ts`) | New room creation returns the `ensureRoom` result directly (201), avoids full table scan |

### 🟢 LOW — Queries & Rate Limiting
| Fix | What changed |
|---|---|
| **2→1 queries** (`db.ts`) | `getMessagesSince` uses single `WHERE rowid > (SELECT rowid WHERE id=?)` query |
| **Unbounded mentions** (`db.ts`) | `getUnreadMentions` capped at `LIMIT 100` (default, backward-compatible) |
| **Rate limiting** (new `rate-limit.ts`) | In-memory sliding-window limiter: 120 req/min per IP, auto-cleanup, no new deps |

### ⏭️ Skipped
**M-3 (mention regex)** — a combined regex approach broke the `@`-prefix requirement and Unicode word-boundary semantics that `mentionMatches` enforces. The original O(n) per-message scan is correct for small clubs.
完成。

